sentences.english: He says officials prevented a showing in Yaounde, the capital.
sentences.chinese: 他說，有關官員阻止影片在喀麥隆首都雅溫得上映。

sentences.english: Laboratory analysis of the specimens is ongoing at the Institut Pasteur in Yaoundé.
sentences.chinese: 雅溫得巴斯德研究所正在對標本作出實驗室分析。

sentences.english: The picture shows the Yaounde Conference Building and its model.
sentences.chinese: 圖爲雅溫得會議大廈及模型。
